flowchart TD
    A[Start main] --> B[Create Cond and Mutex]
    B --> C[Create empty queue]
    C --> D[Loop i from 0 to 9]

    D --> E[Lock mutex]
    E --> F{Queue length equals 2}

    F -->|Yes| G[Wait on condition]
    G --> F

    F -->|No| H[Add item to queue]
    H --> I[Start remove goroutine]
    I --> J[Unlock mutex]
    J --> D

    subgraph RQ
        R1[Sleep 1 second]
        R2[Lock mutex]
        R3[Remove item from queue]
        R4[Print removed message]
        R5[Unlock mutex]
        R6[Signal condition]

        R1 --> R2 --> R3 --> R4 --> R5 --> R6
    end
